    <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\" style=\"font-size:23px\"><strong>Analogy</strong></p>
    \n\n\n\n
    <p class=\"has-text-align-justify\">A Randomized Controlled Experiment is like reaching into an opaque jar to get some candy.</p>
    \n\n\n\n
